  README.md

Example Output
Candidate 1 — FitScore 82, RiskScore 22

Founder-style verdict:

“Strong match. Real systems experience. Resume language looks natural. Missing a bit of Rust/Go depth but overall solid.”

Candidate 2 — FitScore 54, RiskScore 61

Founder-style verdict:

“A lot of JD keywords appear copy-pasted. Claims don’t line up. Risky hire.”

What’s Next (if I continue building this)

PDF → text extraction

Recruiter-style CSV export

Support for multiple JDs (batch mode)

Actual charts (FitScore distribution, skill gaps)

Deployed backend to Deno Deploy / Fly.io

Deployed frontend to Vercel